<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.1.7">
<l>kūnta lārmakiḻ kōvala ṉāyveṇṇey</l>
<l>mānta ḻuntaiyil kaṇṭuma kiḻntupōy</l>
<l>pāntaḷ pāḻiyil paḷḷivi rumpiya</l>
<l>vēnta ṉaicceṉṟu kāṇṭumveḵ kāvuḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having gone, rejoicing, and seen in Aḻuntūr [the one] who ate butter,</l>
<l>Having become a herder whom curly-haired [ladies] enjoyed,</l>
<l>We will go and see in Veḵkā the king</l>
<l>Who relishes a rest on a serpent bed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
